des: "Shrimp lovers and cheese lovers will wrestle for a chance to dip their crackers into this delicious, easy dip!"
ins: In a 9 inch round serving dish, spread the cream cheese. Top with a layer of cocktail sauce. Arrange shrimp evenly over cocktail sauce. Sprinkle Cheddar cheese over all. Chill in the refrigerator approximately 1 hour before serving.
